CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 7, 2008

[Cite as 05/0712008 Case Announcements, 2008-0hio-2028.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2008-0586. Martin v. Ohio Adult Parole Auth.

In Habeas Corpus. On petition for writ of habeas corpus of Robert Martin. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
